subject: Nightclubs and Cabarets
lead_paragraph: The hip hop mogul Jay-Z and a business partner are suing the Red Sox slugger David Ortiz, claiming that Ortiz named his Dominican nightclub after Jay-Z’s chain of 40/40 nightclubs.
